  "detailed_description": "<strong>In this short, retro-style point n' click game,</strong> it's Halloween night and all of Homestar Runner's pals have hidden from him so he can't see their costumes. Explore 9 different locations - collecting items, solving puzzles, and talking to characters - as you help Homestar find all 11 of his dumb animal character friends so he can totally misinterpret their costumes like he always does! <br><br>It's like <strong><i>playing</i></strong> a Homestar Runner Halloween cartoon! That's a good thing, right?!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429100/extras/664c49d51fdef7e97db4d8542dd54eed.poster.avif?t=1693192652\" width=125 height=115 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429100/extras/664c49d51fdef7e97db4d8542dd54eed.webm?t=1693192652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429100/extras/3e329092491120eb1b3dad813ec1aa10.poster.avif?t=1693192652\" width=125 height=145 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429100/extras/3e329092491120eb1b3dad813ec1aa10.webm?t=1693192652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429100/extras/8f5ef00f8b19f5e8e27908ebf00c0bfe.poster.avif?t=1693192652\" width=125 height=145 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429100/extras/8f5ef00f8b19f5e8e27908ebf00c0bfe.webm?t=1693192652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429100/extras/9bbfaf0d041f061864c38c68305e3666.poster.avif?t=1693192652\" width=125 height=115 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429100/extras/9bbfaf0d041f061864c38c68305e3666.webm?t=1693192652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Featuring 100's of lines of <strong>FULLY VOICED</strong> dialog from your fave/not-fave characters from Homestar Runner dot com!<br><br>An optional Secret Quest to complete which unlocks a hidden easter egg.<br><br>All the humor, portmanteaus, and self-indulgent, self-referential jokes you'd expect from Homestar Runner content.",
